{"tid":781993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅芯被指虛假研發 創始人稱「在巨人的肩膀上創新」","createTime":"2018-08-16T10:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T11:36:59.000Z","uid":10338,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4566ccc636ee31751a75adfb92eb8cbba0a4415a","tid":781993,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社１６日專訊》號稱要打造「中國芯」的「國產」瀏覽器紅芯，完成２﹒５億<br />\n元人民幣的Ｃ輪戰略融資，但紅芯融資成功後不足一日，便被網民揭發，紅芯實際上只是<br />\nＣｈｒｏｍｅ瀏覽器的壓縮包，相關內容在微博上被廣泛轉發。<br />\n　　紅芯聯合創始人高婧回應指，承認紅芯瀏覽器「包含Ｃｈｒｏｍｅ在裡面」，但她表示並非<br />\n抄襲，而是「站在巨人的肩膀上去做創新」。她稱紅芯在智慧感知渲染引擎及應用安全方面都進<br />\n行了創新，須連接雲服務。高又堅稱客戶滿意度很高，「絕不是那些人說的拿國產概念去騙錢」<br />\n。<br />\n　　「光明網」評論事件稱，紅芯事件是漢芯事件後又一起以剽竊知識產權為手段，假冒自主創<br />\n新成果的醜聞，且比後者更不堪、更惡劣，表示對藉著「爭光」幌子坑錢騙名的偽創新者及其機<br />\n構，必須繩之以法才能以儆傚尤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7605dc13dc165b8e800d3afe427534a6ad1eac6","tid":781993,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45bb58424123240cddfb7a6e5673261476b54b52","tid":781993,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60dae56fb46c02d5f93f8a88cfa3d4a72671b563","tid":781993,"uid":109173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":